title: Rosie the Riveter WWII Home Front National Historical Park: Be A Junior Ranger
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Kids & Youth     Be A Junior Ranger              Be A Junior Ranger       Junior Ranger Programs  We are currently working on enhancing this page by bringing you more information for Kids activities within our park. We currently offer a Junior Ranger activity for those who would like to participate. To find out more information, please contact the Visitor Education Centerat 510-232-5050.
